  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#x2022; To provide assistance to refugees who are seeking to reunite with their family members and loved ones in Hungary.

&#x2022; To cover the costs of the family reunification administrative procedure, which are prohibitively high for many refugees.

&#x2022; To cover the travel expenses of family members who are trying to reach a Hungarian consulate to lodge a reunification claim.

&#x2022; To cover the travel expenses of family members abroad who have been approved for reunification but must find a way to reach Hungary.

&#x2022; To provide free legal assistance to refugees who are navigating this process.</narrative>
  </description>
